at most of suffering severe brain damage and possibly death 
she does not know what happened and was clearly concerned 
about it and had indicated that she didnt think she would go 
swimming alone again deaton said 
ms jordan was breathing saturday night only with the help of a 
ventilator but sunday the device was gone and she was responding 
