singersongwriter randy vanwarmer is 
counting on the emotional edge of his new album to stem a nineyear 
slide since his millionselling hit just when i needed you most 
the 33yearold vanwarmer has just released i am a 
collection of soft country ballads with romantic titles such as i 
will hold youthats what your smile does for me and words 
i never meant its his first album in four years 
theres something spiritual about the record vanwarmer said 
